snippet.title: Fire Emblem: Dream of Five Trailer 2012
snippet.description:
The trailer of my hack, Fire Emblem: Dream of Five, soon to be released within November, hopefully.
Originally posted for Nintendo Community Fangame Convention.
Go look at the booths of various fan projects here: http://nintendocfc.com/booths.html (Go vote for your favourite projects!)

Place to check out DoF Updates:
http://serenesforest.net/forums/index.php?showtopic=24662&st=0 

Note: This will not be the final version, only Beta V4.
